<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 18:10:34 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列军队无人机袭击约旦河西岸纳布卢斯巴勒斯坦武装分子，17岁青年被打死</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-drone-targets-palestinian-militants-in-west-banks-nablus-17-year-old-killed/00000190-f527-d45d-a5b3-ffaf9d060000</link><description>军方表示，纳布卢斯巴拉塔难民营的袭击目标是武装武装分子，造成一人死亡、多人受伤。以色列安全部门消息人士称，这是对当天早上针对以色列国防军士兵的枪击事件的回应</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 17:48:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-drone-targets-palestinian-militants-in-west-banks-nablus-17-year-old-killed/00000190-f527-d45d-a5b3-ffaf9d060000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事，第 295 天：来自黎巴嫩的火箭弹在以色列北部迈季代勒沙姆斯造成 9 人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-295-rocket-fire-from-lebanon-kills-nine-in-north-israels-majdal-shams/00000190-f4af-dda7-a9f7-f7bfb5bd0000</link><description>戈兰高地 Majdal Shams 镇遭火箭弹袭击，造成 9 名以色列人死亡，伤亡人数最多的是儿童和青少年 ■ 巴勒斯坦人称，以色列国防军的袭击导致汗尤尼斯 (Khan Yunis) 23 人死亡，代尔巴拉学校 (Deir al-Balah) 至少 30 人死亡；以色列国防军：哈马斯利用学校作为指挥中心 ■ 以色列代表团下周前往罗马进行协议谈判 ■ 以色列国防军士兵在检查站受伤；巴勒斯坦卫生部门消息来源：随后的以色列国防军无人机袭击和约旦河西岸冲突导致 17 岁儿童死亡、28 人受伤 ■ 以下是战争进入 295 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 17:16:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-295-rocket-fire-from-lebanon-kills-nine-in-north-israels-majdal-shams/00000190-f4af-dda7-a9f7-f7bfb5bd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列向调解人提出新的加沙协议立场；官员警告称这可能会给谈判带来风险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-presents-new-gaza-deal-position-to-mediators-officials-warn-it-could-risk-talks/00000190-f4f3-dda7-a9f7-f7f703420000</link><description>据以色列外交消息人士称，内塔尼亚胡坚持建立一个机制，阻止巴勒斯坦武装人员从加沙南部进入北部，尽管有人警告称这将危及与哈马斯的谈判</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 17:03:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-presents-new-gaza-deal-position-to-mediators-officials-warn-it-could-risk-talks/00000190-f4f3-dda7-a9f7-f7f703420000</guid></item><item><title>以色列各地数千人集会，家人称内塔尼亚胡正在积极阻止人质交易</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/hostages-families-say-netanyahu-is-deliberately-obstructing-release-deal/00000190-f4ff-dda7-a9f7-f7ff6a350000</link><description>&amp;#39;一切都准备好了，可以继续前进。 “只有内塔尼亚胡在继续破坏这笔交易”，一名人质的母亲说道；以色列最大的城市和数十个地点都发生抗议活动</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 16:57:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/hostages-families-say-netanyahu-is-deliberately-obstructing-release-deal/00000190-f4ff-dda7-a9f7-f7ff6a350000</guid></item><item><title>“因为我们是左派”：在加沙，一名人质预测内塔尼亚胡将推迟迅速释放</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/were-leftists-in-gaza-a-hostage-said-swift-release-was-unlikely-due-to-netanyahu/00000190-f46d-d8b8-a59a-fcff2d880000</link><description>在接受以色列第 12 频道采访时，被释放的人质阿迪娜·莫什 (Adina Moshe) 讲述了查姆·佩里 (Chaim Peri) 在被囚禁期间对她说的话，并描述了一名反抗议者如何在人质交易集会上咒骂她。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 15:57:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/were-leftists-in-gaza-a-hostage-said-swift-release-was-unlikely-due-to-netanyahu/00000190-f46d-d8b8-a59a-fcff2d880000</guid></item><item><title>当地卫生官员称，以色列对加沙中部和南部的空袭造成 50 多人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/health-officials-over-50-killed-in-israeli-airstrikes-in-central-and-southern-gaza/00000190-f45d-d298-a592-fc7f96c30000</link><description>以色列国防军袭击了代尔巴拉赫的一所学校大院，声称这是哈马斯的设施，导致在那里避难的 30 多名巴勒斯坦人被杀。据哈马斯管理的卫生部门称，早先在汗尤尼斯发生的一系列空袭已造成 23 人死亡</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 14:01:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/health-officials-over-50-killed-in-israeli-airstrikes-in-central-and-southern-gaza/00000190-f45d-d298-a592-fc7f96c30000</guid></item><item><title>“我们不必靠刀剑生存”：为什么为和平而战的以色列和巴勒斯坦妇女没有失去希望</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/ten-years-on-israeli-and-palestinian-women-are-still-fighting-for-peace/00000190-ea6a-d8b8-a59a-eefe070c0000</link><description>妇女工资和平组织是在一场加沙战争的阴影下成立的，并在迄今为止最血腥的一场战争中纪念其成立十周年。该组织认为，其加拿大裔以色列联合创始人维维安·西尔弗 (Vivian Silver) 于 10 月 7 日去世，加沙一个巴勒斯坦姐妹组织的多达 40 名成员的死亡只会强调任务的紧迫性</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 11:18:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/ten-years-on-israeli-and-palestinian-women-are-still-fighting-for-peace/00000190-ea6a-d8b8-a59a-eefe070c0000</guid></item><item><title>“对以色列科学的战略打击”：领先学术机构的海外学生数量急剧下降</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/strategic-blow-leading-israeli-academic-institutions-see-sharp-fall-in-foreign-students/00000190-e55e-d59e-a1f5-ffdea7d70000</link><description>加沙战争后，魏茨曼科学研究所和特拉维夫大学的国际博士生和博士后学生数量急剧下降，科学家们现在担心以色列可能会变成像中国或伊朗一样的单一文化国家</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 09:11:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/strategic-blow-leading-israeli-academic-institutions-see-sharp-fall-in-foreign-students/00000190-e55e-d59e-a1f5-ffdea7d70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部 Majdal Shams 的袭击造成 10 人死亡，其中包括儿童；以色列国防军：真主党从黎巴嫩发射火箭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article-live/israeli-jets-attack-hezbollah-targets-in-southern-lebanon-idf-says/00000190-f1ec-dd5f-af93-fbec9c230000</link><description>当地卫生官员称，以色列对加沙中部和南部的空袭造成 50 多人死亡 ■ 官员警告，以色列在加沙谈判上的新立场可能会危及协议 ■ 以色列国防军：向以色列北部发射数十枚火箭弹 ■ 以色列无人机袭击约旦河西岸的纳布卢斯，以回应以色列国防军士兵在检查站遭枪击 ■ 消息人士称，以色列国防军命令汗尤尼斯南部的居民撤离到穆瓦西人道主义区 ■ 消息人士称，摩萨德负责人率领的以色列团队将于下周前往罗马进行人质劫持和停火谈判</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 02:05:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article-live/israeli-jets-attack-hezbollah-targets-in-southern-lebanon-idf-says/00000190-f1ec-dd5f-af93-fbec9c230000</guid></item><item><title>在希伯伦，年轻的巴勒斯坦人在被证明无罪之前被假定有罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-07-27/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/in-hebron-young-palestinians-are-presumed-guilty-until-proven-innocent/00000190-f12f-d8b8-a59a-fdbfcd300000</link><description>两名巴勒斯坦兄弟在深夜在希伯伦被拘留，原因是当地孩子移走了封锁街道的铁丝网；他们被士兵虐待了几个小时。另一名男子因手机上有士兵的照片而遭到殴打并被拘留，他说手机被士兵偷走了</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 23:12:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-07-27/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/in-hebron-young-palestinians-are-presumed-guilty-until-proven-innocent/00000190-f12f-d8b8-a59a-fdbfcd300000</guid></item><item><title>“我希望他们喜欢我。这就是你的生存之道”：莉亚特·阿兹利花了数周时间与绑架她的哈马斯人交谈。这是他们谈论的内容</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/she-spent-weeks-conversing-with-her-hamas-captors-heres-what-they-talked-about/00000190-f0b0-dda7-a9f7-f3b7161b0000</link><description>莉亚特·阿兹利 (Liat Atzili) 于 10 月 7 日在尼尔奥兹基布兹 (Kibbutz Nir ​​Oz) 被绑架，并被哈马斯的两名年轻成员（一名教师和一名律师）扣为人质数周，不知道她的丈夫和三个孩子是否还活着。她所经历的经历与我们迄今为止听说过的经历不同</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 22:33:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/she-spent-weeks-conversing-with-her-hamas-captors-heres-what-they-talked-about/00000190-f0b0-dda7-a9f7-f3b7161b0000</guid></item><item><title>我们属于中东吗？以色列人将黎凡特置于前沿和中心</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/do-we-belong-in-the-middle-east-the-israelis-making-the-levant-relevant-again/00000190-efbc-d8b8-a59a-efbe88670000</link><description>本周，一名年轻女子在加沙失去了祖父，并用歌声纪念了他。此外，特拉维夫电影中心探讨了黑人剥削、Shadi Mar&amp;#39;i 在耶路撒冷电影节上大获全胜，以及为什么一个男人用电锯锯掉了他祖父的画作</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 20:36:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/do-we-belong-in-the-middle-east-the-israelis-making-the-levant-relevant-again/00000190-efbc-d8b8-a59a-efbe88670000</guid></item><item><title>特朗普在佛罗里达州会见内塔尼亚胡时称哈里斯对以色列的言论不尊重</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/meeting-netanyahu-in-florida-trump-says-harris-remarks-on-israel-were-disrespectful/00000190-f039-d298-a592-f83b1e230000</link><description>以色列总理内塔尼亚胡在海湖庄园会见了美国前总统、共和党候选人，并表示以色列代表团将于下周启程，继续进行人质和停火协议谈判</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 18:57:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/meeting-netanyahu-in-florida-trump-says-harris-remarks-on-israel-were-disrespectful/00000190-f039-d298-a592-f83b1e230000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡过时、挥霍的飞机必须下架</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-07-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahus-outdated-profligate-plane-has-to-go/00000190-ef22-d298-a592-ff3395bf0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 18:26:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-07-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahus-outdated-profligate-plane-has-to-go/00000190-ef22-d298-a592-ff3395bf0000</guid></item><item><title>摩萨德负责人率领的以色列团队将于下周前往罗马进行人质和停火谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-team-led-by-mossad-chief-to-travel-to-rome-next-week-for-hostage-cease-fire-talks/00000190-f03a-d541-adbc-f9fa03da0000</link><description>总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡在佛罗里达州与美国前总统唐纳德·特朗普会面时证实了这一信息，并表示代表团将“可能在本周初”离开</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 18:18:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-team-led-by-mossad-chief-to-travel-to-rome-next-week-for-hostage-cease-fire-talks/00000190-f03a-d541-adbc-f9fa03da0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 294 天：约旦河西岸哈马斯领导人在以色列拘留期间死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-294-hamas-leader-in-west-bank-dies-in-israeli-custody/00000190-efec-d298-a592-ffff56670001</link><description>据报道，以色列正在寻求改变当前的停战提议 ■ 以色列高级谈判代表表示，内塔尼亚胡故意试图让停战谈判陷入危机 ■ 尸体被哈马斯扣押的以色列人的父亲表示，拜登向俘虏家属表示“希望未来几天会发生一些事情” ” ■ 英国不会挑战国际刑事法院对总理内塔尼亚胡和国防部长加兰特发出逮捕令的管辖权 ■ 这是战争进入第 294 天时您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 16:49:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-294-hamas-leader-in-west-bank-dies-in-israeli-custody/00000190-efec-d298-a592-ffff56670001</guid></item><item><title>“拿人质的生命做赌注”：以色列高级谈判代表称内塔尼亚胡故意在停火谈判中制造危机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/senior-israeli-negotiator-says-netanyahu-knowingly-creating-crisis-in-cease-fire-talks/00000190-ef5c-dda7-a9f7-ef7f7b210000</link><description>一名参与人质交易谈判的以色列高级官员告诉国土报，内塔尼亚胡要求建立一个防止武装人员进入加沙地带北部的机制，这是“对谈判的致命打击”</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 15:07:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/senior-israeli-negotiator-says-netanyahu-knowingly-creating-crisis-in-cease-fire-talks/00000190-ef5c-dda7-a9f7-ef7f7b210000</guid></item><item><title>英国不会追究国际刑事法院对内塔尼亚胡逮捕令的质疑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/u-k-wont-pursue-intl-criminal-court-challenge-to-netanyahu-arrest-warrant/00000190-eef0-d298-a592-fef3b3ad0000</link><description>英国政府正式宣布推翻前政府对国际刑事法院管辖权提出质疑的政策 ■ 一位以色列高级官员告诉《国土报》，“这是一个根本错误的决定，它扭曲了正义和真理，侵犯了所有民主国家的权利”打击恐怖主义。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 12:46:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/u-k-wont-pursue-intl-criminal-court-challenge-to-netanyahu-arrest-warrant/00000190-eef0-d298-a592-fef3b3ad0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙地带南部丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-strip/00000190-eded-d45d-a5b3-efef90a90000</link><description>37岁，下士。 （res.）莫蒂·拉夫（Moti Rave）是一名推土机操作员，也是两个女孩的父亲，于周四被杀</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 08:41:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-strip/00000190-eded-d45d-a5b3-efef90a90000</guid></item><item><title>官员表示，以色列对英国新政府对国际刑事法院逮捕令的立场感到失望</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-disappointed-with-new-u-k-govts-position-on-icc-arrest-warrants-official-says/00000190-ed70-d541-adbc-fdf01c500000</link><description>以色列高级官员表示，工党政府决定撤销国际刑事法院对总理内塔尼亚胡和加兰特的逮捕令的保留，对此深感失望</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 06:32:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-disappointed-with-new-u-k-govts-position-on-icc-arrest-warrants-official-says/00000190-ed70-d541-adbc-fdf01c500000</guid></item></channel></rss>